{"tid":963054,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論】係咪所有嘢都係對立，除咗真理？","createTime":"2018-12-31T10:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T09:09:43.000Z","uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8c6a281d24a3074aedfdea15a0ed6489fc35f3","tid":963054,"uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"忽發其想喺度諗，係咪所有嘢都係對立，即係正反咁，或者好似一個平面咁，可以代表矛盾或者係分歧。<br />\n<br />\n而真理唔存在對立、分歧、矛盾等等，好似一個球體咁。球體冇前後之分，冇對立之分，只有光滑嘅表面。如果真理存在矛盾，咁佢仲係唔係真理？真理係咪唔會有被反駁到嘅論點？真理可唔可以完全反駁質疑真理嘅論點？<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識&ldquo;哲學&ldquo;。唔知算唔算哲學問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff3415f4afed4220965cb5e2fb96091efe6184b","tid":963054,"uid":202131,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGCZVsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGCZVsf.jpg&h=9c88f2b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ae508a3d196443937e7b2944036c4fb9944a40d","tid":963054,"uid":228049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"歪理？"},{"pid":"d85324cabf27c94406a4217ce06265ab39387f94","tid":963054,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"打開咗真理之門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7d7d6c1d57d4ba842552941b05738a3f2be744","tid":963054,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:26:51.000Z","msg":"所有嘢都係對立？<br />\n所有嘢都有對立？"},{"pid":"9ab7a5daba29cbfd8738fc1ac519aeb738d69381","tid":963054,"uid":79372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T12:43:45.000Z","msg":"若絕對性嘅真理存在，其必然係超越性，若輕鬆用人有限嘅認知與邏輯，以可以完全由人去掌握嘅假設下去論斷真理，必然會得到某定程度上錯誤嘅理解"},{"pid":"c984e6e822e644d0d1eccd8a5317e03e1583422e","tid":963054,"uid":17301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇野係絕對既真理，人類所謂既真理係建基於自己既角