理。<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"即係話真理有機會隨時間而改變？"},{"pid":"0fe0ea0b92912a36f0442d31cdeae5b32724b6b8","tid":963054,"uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3be8569cd719a11c33832b094eaf97431e9605e","tid":963054,"uid":52122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T13:58:04.000Z","msg":"咩係真理？<br />\n我覺得勝者先係真理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:17:13.000Z","msg":"真理係咪事物嘅核心？例如我地今時睇嘢只係睇到表面，表面之下先係真理。好似冰層咁。"},{"pid":"80805f8c777baf3be4d82ea5e6c2c79db7b130d0","tid":963054,"uid":216477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6be5668aabb11506b64f24d7606940f9ce128fc9","tid":963054,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"講出咩叫真理先有得傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又如果你先假設真理係有XXXX因素<br />\n咁即係將真理排除在外<br />\n因為冇嗰樣野就唔係真理一部份<br />\n咁真理又會係真理咩<br />\n所以乜野先係真理係一個好重要嘅問題"},{"pid":"9731200a5f34f1fe60adb35d2bb99f5605f4cd3d","tid":963054,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:22:30.000Z","msg":"上面有人話歪理就係真理嘅對立<br />\n但若果真理係將歪理考慮過先推到出嚟<br />\n可能呢個先係真理<br />\n咁真理可能真係包含一切包括歪理"},{"pid":"bfa0e5444fab7b7343a153f7fe444d0e730d7f60","tid":963054,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"啲細路會用鋼煉套卡通嚟答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c530975439165b76f2f6045f501c7f66243c91","tid":963054,"uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfa0e5444fab7b7343a153f7fe444d0e730d7f60","tid":963054,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"啲細路會用鋼煉套卡通嚟答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <